name: Incompleted (ONCGM, CiscG, Richard Pierre Gayer, Alvaro_Eltz)
name_original: Incompleted (ONCGM, CiscG, Richard Pierre Gayer, Alvaro_Eltz)
description:
Your unexplained objective is to collect all doors in the game.

Keyboard controls:

A - D and Arrows to move.
Space to jump and to wall jump.
R to respawn at the last checkpoint.
T to  restart the game.

Xbox controller:

Left joystick to move.
A to jump and to wall jump.
Start to respawn at the last checkpoint.
Back to  restart the game.

Made by:
Elias (ONCGM) Pereira
Richard Pierre Gayer
Álvaro Eltz
